\f0\fs24 \cf0 This work implements a visual analysis system containing a map view, radar view, calendar selector, social network view, and base view. Among them, the map supports multi-class feature joint selection filtering and cross-sectional distribution display for demographics. The social network view supports searching for social relationships of specific people and displaying the k-means clustering visualization results of their related people. The calendar view, radar map and base view work together to display the time-series characteristics of the base derived from HDBSCAN. }

